President Obama has nominated Judge David C. Nye to serve on the United States District Court for the District of Idaho. Judge Nye has been a District Judge for Idaho's Sixth Judicial District Court since 2007. Prior to his appointment, he worked at the law firm of Merrill & Merrill, Chartered, specializing in medical malpractice and insurance law. He began his legal career as a law clerk and obtained his J.D. from J. Reuben Clark Law School at Brigham Young University.